#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:338
msgid "FooEvents POS is a web-based point of sale plugin for WooCommerce that runs on your own server and enables you to sell and print tickets in-person (this functionality requires the FooEvents for WooCommerce plugin to be installed and activated)."
msgstr "FooEvents POS is 'n aanlyn punt van verkoping-inprop vir WooCommerce wat op jou eie bediener loop en jou in staat stel om kaartjies in persoon te verkoop en druk (hierdie funksionaliteit vereis dat die FooEvents vir WooCommerce-inprop geïnstalleer en geaktiveer word)."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:339
msgid "FooEvents POS is a point of sale (POS) system for WooCommerce that turns any computer, iPad or Android tablet into a physical retail platform. FooEvents POS apps connect to your WooCommerce store using the FooEvents POS plugin and enable you to sell your products in person while accepting payments using Square™ and Stripe™ or manually using any third-party card reader."
msgstr "FooEvents POS is 'n punt van verkoop (POS) stelsel vir WooCommerce wat enige rekenaar, iPad of Android tablet omskep in 'n fisiese kleinhandelplatform. FooEvents POS-toepassings verbind met jou WooCommerce-winkel deur die FooEvents POS-inprop en stel jou in staat om jou produkte persoonlik te verkoop terwyl jy betalings aanvaar met Square™ en Stripe™ of handmatig met enige derde-party kaartleser."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:340
msgid "FooEvents POS is a point of sale (POS) that turns any WooCommerce store into a secure omnichannel retail platform which allows you to sell online and in-person seamlessly. Process payments directly within the FooEvents POS point of sale (POS) apps using Square™ and Stripe™ or manually using any third-party card reader. Keep your online and physical store synced in real time without any other software!"
msgstr "FooEvents POS vir WooCommerce is 'n verkooppunt (POS) wat enige WooCommerce-winkel omskep in 'n veilige omnichannel kleinhandelsplatform wat jou toelaat om aanlyn en persoonlik naadloos te verkoop. Verwerk betalings direk binne die FooEvents POS-verkooppunt (POS)-toepassings met behulp van Square™ en Stripe™ of handmatig met enige derde-party kaartleser. Hou jou aanlyn- en fisiese winkel in werklikheid gesinkroniseer sonder enige ander sagteware!"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:341
msgid "Show all categories"
msgstr "Wys alle kategorieë."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:342
msgid "Only show products from these specific categories"
msgstr "Toon slegs produkte uit hierdie spesifieke kategorieë."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:343
msgid "Submit a Review"
msgstr "Plaas 'n Resensie."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:344
msgid "Please take a moment to share your experience on Trustpilot—your feedback helps us to improve, grow and provide an even better product!"
msgstr "Neem asseblief 'n oomblik om jou ervaring op Trustpilot te deel—jou terugvoer help ons om te verbeter, te groei en 'n nog beter produk te bied!"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:345
msgid "Thank you for using FooEvents POS!"
msgstr "Dankie vir die gebruik van FooEvents POS!"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:346
msgid "Order statuses"
msgstr "Bestellingsituasies"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:347
msgid "Select the order statuses that should trigger a new order alert in the POS app when new or updated orders are fetched in the background."
msgstr "Kies die bestellingsstatusse wat 'n nuwe bestellingswaarskuwing in die POS-toep wanneer nuwe of opgedateerde bestellings in die agtergrond opgehaal word."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:348
msgid "Shipping methods"
msgstr "Versendingsmetodes"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:349
msgid "Select the shipping methods that should trigger a new order alert in the POS app when new or updated orders are fetched in the background."
msgstr "Kies die versendingsmetodes wat 'n nuwe bestellingswaarskuwing in die POS-toep wanneer nuwe of opgedateerde bestellings in die agtergrond opgehaal word."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:350
msgid "Billing address title"
msgstr "Faktureringsadres titel"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:351
msgid "Title of the billing address (e.g. \"Billing Address\")."
msgstr "Titel van die faktuuradres (bv. \"Faktuuradres\")."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:352
msgid "Quantity step amount"
msgstr "Hoeveelheidsstapbedrag"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:354
#, php-format
msgid "Specify the amount that this product's quantity can be increased or decreased in the cart e.g. 1 or 0.01, 0.5 etc. The current default value is \"%1$s\"."
msgstr "Spesifiseer die bedrag waarmee die hoeveelheid van hierdie produk in die mandjie verhoog of verlaag kan word, bv. 1 of 0.01, 0.5 ens. Die huidige verstekwaarde is \"%1$s\"."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:355
msgid "Cart quantity unit"
msgstr "Kartheenheidseenheid"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:356
msgid "Specify the unit used for this product's cart quantity e.g. kg, lb, inches etc. This value can also be left blank which will result in no unit being displayed."
msgstr "Spesifiseer die eenheid wat gebruik word vir die produk se karthoeveelheid bv. kg, lb, duim ens. Hierdie waarde kan ook leeg gelaat word wat sal lei tot geen eenheid wat vertoon word."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:357
msgid "Confirm stock availability at checkout"
msgstr "Bevestig voorraadbeskikbaarheid by die afrekenpunt."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:358
msgid "Perform a final stock check for the products in the cart before submitting the order to WooCommerce or sending a payment request to Stripe or Square which may slow down the checkout process. Please note that the background data fetch will still update stock quantities at the frequency set in the FooEvents POS app."
msgstr "Voer 'n finale voorraadondersoek vir die produkte in die mandjie uit voordat die bestelling na WooCommerce gestuur word of 'n betalingsversoek na Stripe of Square gestuur word wat die afrekeningsproses kan vertraag. Let asseblief daarop dat die agtergronddata-opvraag steeds voorraad hoeveelhede sal opdateer teen die frekwensie wat in die FooEvents POS-toepassing ingestel is."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:359
msgid "Customer user role"
msgstr "Kliëntgebruikersrol"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:360
msgid "The FooEvents POS app will only fetch users with the selected roles. This can be customized by selecting other user role(s) in the multi-select box."
msgstr "Die FooEvents POS-program sal slegs gebruikers met die gekose rolle ophaal. Dit kan aangepas word deur ander gebruikersrol(le) in die multi-kieskas te kies."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:361
msgid "Default quantity step amount"
msgstr "Standaard hoeveelheid stap bedrag"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:362
msgid "Specify the default amount that a product's quantity can be increased or decreased in the cart."
msgstr "Spesifiseer die verstekbedrag wat 'n produk se hoeveelheid in die mandjie verhoog of verlaag kan word."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:363
msgid "Default cart quantity unit"
msgstr "Standaard mandjie hoeveelheid eenheid"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:364
msgid "Specify the default unit used for product cart quantities e.g. kg, lb, inches etc. This value can be overriden at a product level."
msgstr "Spesifiseer die verstek eenheid wat gebruik word vir produkkarhoeveelhede bv. kg, lb, duim ens. Hierdie waarde kan op produkvlak oorskryf word."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:365
msgid "Default minimum cart quantity"
msgstr "Standaard minimum mandjie hoeveelheid"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:366
msgid "Specify the default minimum amount that can be added to the cart for products."
msgstr "Spesifiseer die verstek minimum bedrag wat by die mandjie vir produkte gevoeg kan word."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:367
msgid "Default customer"
msgstr "Standaard kliënt"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:368
msgid "Select the customer that should be used by default for any new orders created in the FooEvents POS app."
msgstr "Kies die kliënt wat standaard gebruik moet word vir enige nuwe bestellings wat in die FooEvents POS-toepassing geskep word."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:369
msgid "Default submit order status"
msgstr "Standaard indien bestellingsstatus"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:370
msgid "Set the default status that orders should have when submitting via the POS."
msgstr "Stel die verstekstatus wat bestellings moet hê wanneer dit via die POS ingedien word."

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:371
msgid "Disable new order emails"
msgstr "Deaktiveer nuwe bestellings e-posse"

#: admin/helpers/fooeventspos-phrases-helper.php:372
